data.description: Welcome to Carriage Row Townhomes. Enjoy open concept living in this 2-story townhome. Soak up the warmth of a wood fire in your spacious living room. Beautifully updated kitchen will please the chef in the home w/granite countertops & shaker style cabinets. Enjoy slide out cabinet drawers, spice rack, & trash bin. SS appl, spacious pantry, & breakfast bar for quick meals or buffet style meals w/guests.  Add'l dining space perfect for everyday or more formal gatherings.  Primary BR w/ensuite bath, guest BR, guest bath, & laundry rm w/tons of storage finish off the interior of this home. Enjoy the outdoor space off LR w/storage. Individual garage, Federal Way Schools, easy access to freeways, shops, lake, & Star Lake LL Rail in '24.
